## Quickstart

To install run the following:

```bash
pip install sphinx-thumb-image
```

To use in Sphinx simply add to your `conf.py`:

```python
extensions = ["sphinx_thumb_image"]
```

And in your Sphinx documents:

```rst
.. thumb-image:: pictures/photo.jpg
    :resize-width: 100px
```
